Rapier with Piercer and Magic Weapon in Offhand - Unnested Macros - Works on it's own, but not in a nested query
---------------------------------------------
Rapier-Piercer-Dex-MW-Offhand-Standard
&{template:default} {{name=Melee Attack - Rapier}} {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes an Offhand Rapier attack*}} [[ [[ [[1d8!cf<1cs>8[Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[1 [Magic Weapon]]] [Magic Weapon] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Piercing}} {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies}} {{Static=$[[3]] Piercing + $[[4]] Varies}} {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** }} {{Static Total=$[[6]] ***Static Damage*** }} {{Total=$[[7]] **Total Damage** }} {{Piercer Hit=Once per turn when you hit a creature with an attack that deals piercing damage you can reroll one of the attack's damage dice and you must use the new roll. }} {{Piercer Crit= On a critical - deal an additional [[1d8cf<0cs>100]] Piercing}}
---------------------------------------------
